<p>&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;</p>
<div align="left">
<div align="justify">     For over 20 years of foundation and development, Phu Tho Pharmaceutical College has trained thousands of people working in health care sector in Viet Nam. In the context of international integration and powerful development of Viet Nam pharmaceutical industry, College has recently had a positive innovation in management and improved the training quality to meet the need of enterprises and society.<br />
<strong>Building the Brand Name</strong><br />
The college was initially called a training establishment of pharmacy, then upgraded to Center of Training Pharmacy, then under the name Pharmaceutical Technical School, Intermediate School of Pharmacy and now called Phu Tho Pharmaceutical College. Thus, the college has confirmed its rapid growth. The number of students increases through years. Being supported by Provincial Party, People&#8217;s Committee of Phu Tho province, leaders of ministries and Prime Minister, Phu Tho Pharmaceutical College is planning to upgrade to Pharmacy University. During that period of development, the staff members have been persistent and diligent in training career with a commitment to the highest quality. The brand name has been confirmed because students from 60 provinces over the country come to study at College, 95% of graduated students are employed. The majority of candidates for pharmaceutical civil servants in many provinces graduated from College. In some other provinces, that number is 100%. Especially, in some areas students from Phu Tho Pharmaceutical College are at a top priority of employment.<br />
<strong>Building the infrastructure</strong><br />
College has 2 campuses which cover the area of nearly 24 hectares (campus 1: nearly 2ha; campus 2: 22ha) with airy space. On the grounds are classrooms, experiment laboratories, library, playgrounds, swimming-pool, canteens, cafeteria, post-office, hostel, ATM booth, etc which are synchronously constructed. Specially, the difference between College and the other ones is that there is a pharmaceutical company and a pharmaceutical manufacturing enterprise in the campus which achieve the international standards GMP. Facilities such as electronic library, digital library, internet, Wi-Fi, projectors, computers, spectrometers, liquid chromatography, solubility testing machines, sub meters, PH meters, tabletting machines, milling machines, grinding machines are equipped to ensure that students can study in practice. It also links between College and enterprises to give students chances to find a good job after graduating.<br />
<strong>Building an enthusiastic teaching staff</strong><br />
Phu Tho Pharmaceutical College has a teaching staff of nearly 700 lecturers and thousands of practical guides from Pharmaceutical Company, all of them are always in solidarity and absorbed in science researches. There are 13 Professors and Associate Professors, 50 Doctors, nearly 200 Masters working in College. Seventeen teachers are studying for PhD in France and Korea. All the other teachers are required to study master to meet the quality of training.<br />
Scientific work is one of the strengths of Phu Tho Pharmaceutical College. We also pay great attention to scientific research, transferring technologies from the projects to Phu Tho Pharmaceutical Company, College and other enterprises. In 2013, there were 137 scientific research programs in school level, provincial level and national level.<br />
<strong>Promote cooperation in training</strong><br />
In the context of international integration, a great emphasis is placed on international collaboration. College not only has foreign teachers but also sends students and lecturers to study abroad. College has international partners from France, Germany, Australia, Switzerland, China, Russia, Japan, Korea, Taiwan, etc with the objective of achieving international training quality.<br />
For what has been done for over 20 years of  development, Phu Tho Pharmaceutical College has been awarded The Labor Order, Gold Symbol of Viet Nam human resource training, Certificates of Merit from Prime Minister, Ministers and Departments. That College has innovation in management and improvement in training quality is shining our faith.</p>
